{"tid":2338043,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人N個]上過神枱變幕後操盤搞到成pat屎既傳聞","createTime":"2020-12-23T17:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T02:24:55.000Z","uid":66173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80125393f939d6ad2cee7e57116eacbe9dd36650","tid":2338043,"uid":66173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"1. 王家衛：傳聞擺渡人掛名監製實際導演，齣戲爛左掛名導演張嘉佳食曬死貓<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>《擺渡人》原本是編導張嘉佳一篇不足五千字、用第一人稱寫的短篇小說，主要是借敘事者之口述說酒客小玉和馬力的故事，其長度和厚度都不足以支撐一部超過兩小時的劇情片。王家衛答允充當監製（據說也實質做了不少導演的工作）和編劇後，對原文本作出關鍵的增修，包括：</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/文摘/article/20170102/s00022/1483321185139/【影評】擺渡人的自詡與不見（文-朗天）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%96%87%E6%91%98%2Farticle%2F20170102%2Fs00022%2F1483321185139%2F%E3%80%90%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E3%80%91%E6%93%BA%E6%B8%A1%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E8%A9%A1%E8%88%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%A9%EF%BC%89&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=02e2954f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%96%87%E6%91%98%2Farticle%2F20170102%2Fs00022%2F1483321185139%2F%E3%80%90%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E3%80%91%E6%93%BA%E6%B8%A1%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E8%A9%A1%E8%88%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%A9%EF%BC%89&h=aa5c06a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/文摘/article/20170102/s00022/1483321185139/【影評】擺渡人的自詡與不見（文-朗天）</a><br />\n<br />\n2. Phil Jackson: 傳喺紐約人做總裁搶埋教練個post 推三角戰術，主力Melo同Rose都唔受落；佢主理既draft同交易決定都好差<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ianbegley/status/840254972923015168?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianbegley%2Fstatus%2F840254972923015168%3Fs%3D21&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=a6a24ddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianbegley%2Fstatus%2F840254972923015168%3Fs%3D21&h=7c146dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ianbegley/status/840254972923015168?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇其他神枱級既人去左幕後操盤但回曬塘既例子？<br />\n通常好彩地因為退居左幕後 孭飛唔會第一時間提起佢<br />\n咩介別都得 前提係要上過神枱 齋幕後操控唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2eb602afd02ca848eef197db50329f906d638ed","tid":2338043,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"掉轉就聽過 <br />\n香港有史以來最多人睇嘅戲<br />\n《最佳拍檔》係吳準少掛名導演<br />\n但所有文戲武戲都係由其他大導代勞"},{"pid":"dd9af41d4aa91669dcf4f7819a8c29f4b81fd8a8","tid":2338043,"uid":14275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:25:49.000Z","msg":"周星星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1937dbc9cdeda95ab6d080eb13775852f6822e","tid":2338043,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2eb602afd02ca848eef197db50329f906d638ed","tid":2338043,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"掉轉就聽過 <br />\n香港有史以來最多人睇嘅戲<br />\n《最佳拍檔》係吳準少掛名導演<br />\n但所有文戲武戲都係由其他大導代勞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:24:55.000Z","msg":"果時都出得起800萬budget 而家啲戲計返通漲都未必有咁多budget"}]}